The paper discusses the challenges and solutions related to the deployment of monitoring drones for security-sensitive areas. This involves the use of various technologies such as detection, tracking, localization, and routing schemes, which are relevant to the sub-categories of computer security (cs.CR), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
